345
00:42:21,500 --> 00:42:22,666
I want to make money.

346
00:42:31,833 --> 00:42:35,583
Do you know what drives people to fight?

347
00:42:40,333 --> 00:42:41,333
Hunger.

348
00:42:47,000 --> 00:42:48,000
