that I still exist.

491
01:00:14,958 --> 01:00:20,750
Don't ever give me the feeling
that you think you're better than me,

492
01:00:22,125 --> 01:00:25,208
because I can have you replaced
in a second.

493
01:00:25,916 --> 01:00:27,000
